  <div class="row featurette container-fluid" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-bottom" data-aos-duration="1000">
    <div class="col-md-10 order-md-2">
      <h4>What features can I avail during the video call?</h4>
      <li class="help-list"><b>1. User Names :</b> On hovering over a video box you can see that user’s name.</li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>2. Sound Alerts :</b> When somebody joins you will be alerted with a sound. Isn't that cool?</li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>3. On/Off Video :</b> You can click on this icon and your video will not be visible to others instead your initials will be and clicking again will make your video visible.</li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>4. Mute/Unmute Audio :</b> You can click on this icon and mute yourself and clicking again unmute yourself.</li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>5. Mute All :</b> You can mute everyone except yourself in the call </li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>6. Raise/Lower Hand :</b> You can click on this icon and a red box and a hand beside your name will be visible to all users and clicking this again will undo that.</li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>7. Participants :</b> On clicking this icon you can see the list of all participants in the call and clicking outside the list bar will minimise the list</li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>8. Chat : </b>On clicking this icon your chat bar will open and you can chat their, whenever a person will text you on the call the chat bar will automatically open and to close it you can click anywhere outside the chat bar
        will minimise it.</li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>9. Screen Sharing :</b> On clicking this icon a new tab will open where you will be given the option what you want to share, on choosing that you can share your screen and for all the other users they will get a link to your screen.</li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>10. Collab :</b> This a feature using which the users can draw together, create ideas and just go wild.</li>
      <li class="help-list"><b>11. End Call :</b> This will end your call and redirect you to the proper page.</li>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-2 order-md-1">
