      <h5>Signing Up allows you to</h5>
      <li class="help-list">1. Create groups of people you have meets often and is not a one time thing.</li>
      <li class="help-list">2. In every group you can add meets and this will send the members a mail about the meet</li>
      <li class="help-list">3. You will have a history of all the meets you have </li>
      <li class="help-list">4. and also store the chats before, after and during the meet.</li>
      <li class="help-list">5. Get reminders mails before your meet.</li>

    </div>
    <div class="col-md-3 order-md-2">
