  <div class="row featurette container-fluid" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-bottom" data-aos-duration="1000">
    <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
      <h4>How to SignUp or LogIn?</h4>
      <h5>If you are already not a registered user</h5>
      <li class="help-list">1. Click on Sign Up</li>
      <li class="help-list">2. Fill your details, make sure to fill a valid email Id or else you won’t get mails</li>
      <li class="help-list">3. And that’s it and you will be redirected to your dashboard which will be empty now and you have to create or join groups.</li>
      <br>
      <h5>If you are a registered user</h5>
      <li class="help-list">1. Click on Log In</li>
      <li class="help-list">2. Enter the email-id and password and you will be redirected to your dashboard.</li>

    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
      <img src="/images/signup.png" alt="" style="padding-right:20px;" width="400" height="400" aria-label="Placeholder: 400x400">

