  <div class="row featurette container-fluid" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-anchor-placement="top-bottom" data-aos-duration="1000">
    <div class="col-md-7 order-md-1">
      <h4>How to create groups? <strong>(Only available if logged in)</strong></h4>
      <li class="help-list">1. To create groups click on the plus button on top of your list of groups or in your navbar.</li>
      <li class="help-list">2. Give your group an unique name and a key.</li>
      <li class="help-list">3. Share that key with people you want in that group.</li>

      <h4>How to join groups? </h4>
      <li class="help-list">1. To join group click on the first button above the list of groups or the join group link on the navbar.</li>
      <li class="help-list">2. Enter the group name and the group key.</li>
      <li class="help-list">3. That’s it. What are you waiting for?</li>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5 order-md-2">
      <img src="/images/creategroup.png" alt="" style="padding-right:20px;" width="400" height="400" aria-label="Placeholder: 400x400">

