    <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
      <h4>Forgot the group key and your friends are waiting?</h4>
      <p>Don’t worry we got you covered.</p>
      <li class="help-list">1. Open your dashboard and click on the group you want the key of.</li>
      <li class="help-list">2. Click on the controls button in the bottom</li>
      <li class="help-list">3. Choose group details</li>
      <li class="help-list">4. Voila!! You can see the group key as well the list of people you share the group with.</li>

      <h4>How to create a new meet?</h4>
      <li class="help-list">1. Open your dashboard and click on the group you want the key of. </li>
      <li class="help-list">2. Click on the new meet button in the bottom </li>
      <li class="help-list">3. Fill all the details and all the members will receive the info about the new meet. </li>
    </div>
