      <h4>How to cancel a meet?</h4>
      <p> Click on the cancel meet option on the meet box and there you go - everybody will receive a mail of cancellation.</p>

      <h4> Cancelled a meet by mistake? </h4>
      <p> Click on undo cancel and everything is back to normal.</p>

      <h4> Want to remind everybody to be on time for the meet?</h4>
      <p> Click on the remind button on the meet box and everyone will receive the reminder. <strong>Also we will remind every member about the meet automatically so don't you worry!</strong></p>

      <h4>Want to read old chats or just read what your friends chatted during the call?</h4>
      <p> Click on the chat button on the meet box and voila… you can infact continue talking there.</p>

